and Champagne et Chocolat

1)Champagne et Chocolat at the French Embassy  
Feb. 8th, Saturday Evening
More Chocolate, More Chefs, More Champagne!

2)DC Restaurant Week, Jan. 13th-19th
Top Restaurants at $20.03 for Lunch and $30.03 for Dinner!

3)Fifth Annual Fine Art of Cuisine at the Ritz Carlton
22 seminars, 16 participating chefs and over 200 wines!
Jan. 17th-19th, Ritz Carlton Tyson’s Corner

